	Have Automake check NEWS and use bzip2

	* configure.ac (AM_INIT_AUTOMAKE): Add options check-news and
	dist-bzip2.

2009-08-25  Daniel Elstner  <danielk@openismus.com>

	Update NEWS for libsigc++ 2.2.4 release

